name atenddvi
category Package
revision 79461
shortdesc Provides the \AtEndDvi command
longdesc This package is unneeded and does nothing when used with a
longdesc LaTeX format 2020-10-01 or newer as in this case the format
longdesc provides the \AtEndDvi command. For older formats it implements
longdesc \AtEndDvi, a counterpart to \AtBeginDvi. The execution of its
longdesc argument is delayed to the end of the document at the end of
longdesc the last page. Thus \special and \write remain effective,
longdesc because they are put into the last page. This is the main
longdesc difference to \AtEndDocument.
